column5: 29 1/4 in the net, no tail pinch.  Came on on the 7 colour on a hot day with a bit of a wound, so it was quick snap, measure and release. Go make some more mamma not a pb, but darn close
Gawd, that is one ugly mug.  The fish I mean

When I seen your post, I said ya right, yer pushing 50. LOL That is one long eye, but man does it have some nasty blemish.

in the furniture business, we used to call those Character Marks   She is definitely an old warhorse. No idea how the wound happened, I actually didn't see it until I had the photo developed -  did spit the hook once she was in the net, so maybe brushed that. ?
